        "resolucion": [
               "<strong>1) Hallamos los puntos de intersección.</strong>",
              "Igualamos f(x)=g(x):",
              "$$x^2-3x+1=2x-3$$",
              "$$x^2-5x+4=0$$",
              "Factorizamos:",
              "$$(x-1)(x-4)=0$$",
              "Entonces:",
              "$$x=1 \\quad \\text{y} \\quad x=4$$",
          
              "<strong>2) Determinamos cuál función está arriba en el intervalo [1,4].</strong>",
              "Calculamos la diferencia:",
              "$$f(x)-g(x)=x^2-3x+1-(2x-3)$$",
              "$$=x^2-5x+4$$",
              "Probamos un punto intermedio, por ejemplo x=2:",
              "$$f(2)=4-6+1=-1$$",
              "$$g(2)=4-3=1$$",
              "Entonces g(x) > f(x) en el intervalo.",
          
              "<strong>3) Planteamos el área entre curvas.</strong>",
              "$$A=\\int_{1}^{4} [g(x)-f(x)] dx$$",
              "$$=\\int_{1}^{4} \\left[(2x-3)-(x^2-3x+1)\\right] dx$$",
          
              "Simplificamos el integrando:",
              "$$=\\int_{1}^{4} (-x^2+5x-4) dx$$",
          
              "<strong>4) Integramos.</strong>",
              "$$\\int (-x^2+5x-4)dx=-\\frac{x^3}{3}+\\frac{5x^2}{2}-4x$$",
          
              "<strong>5) Evaluamos entre 1 y 4.</strong>",
              "En x=4:",
              "$$-\\frac{64}{3}+\\frac{80}{2}-16$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{64}{3}+40-16$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{64}{3}+24$$",
              "$$=\\frac{8}{3}$$",
          
              "En x=1:",
              "$$-\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}-4$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{1}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}-\\frac{12}{3}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{13}{3}+\\frac{5}{2}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{26}{6}+\\frac{15}{6}$$",
              "$$=-\\frac{11}{6}$$",
          
              "Restamos:",
              "$$A=\\frac{8}{3}-(-\\frac{11}{6})$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{16}{6}+\\frac{11}{6}$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{27}{6}$$",
              "$$A=\\frac{9}{2}$$",
          
              "<strong>Conclusión.</strong>",
              "El área encerrada entre las curvas es:",
              "$$A=\\frac{9}{2}$$"
        ]
